name: GODMODE.WAD
description:
"On Daemon moon there is a gateway to Hell.
Has already been opened and they have entered.
From both worlds to both sides. 

My friends! My soldiers! They murder to themselves!
Possessed by spectres that whisper at my side!
I hear then conspire against humanity,
(And I don't know what can I do,
if run away or drive insane)."

Doom shareware modding to enable endless shooting me in my faces.
